        img(src="/images/2.jpg")
        h6.title Josephine, 22
        h6.job Model
        p For me, its plain simple. It's just anything will do.
        .interests
          span Eat
          span Drink
          span Travel
        hr
        span.like-button Let's Match
    .content-background#rachel-content
      .content
        i.fas.fa-times.close-button
        img(src="/images/3.jpg")
        h6.title Rachel Gray, 21
        h6.job Author
